This documentation describes Event Alerts for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF). Event Alerts sends notifications
via email to CF users.

## <a id='overview'></a>Overview

PCF Event Alerts is a service that reads events from the firehose and turns them into email notifications
sent to CF users.

## <a id='features'></a>Key Features

Event Alerts includes the following key features:

* Send an email to a specific CF user.
* Send emails to users within a specific CF space.

